    (competency_question) (competency_question) CQ7: What were good vintages for Napa Zinfandel?
    (competency_question) (competency_question) CQnew1: What grapes are used to make Bordeaux wine?</dc:source>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#WineVintage">
